name: ApiStoreType

api.authToken.description:
authToken coupled to device, set by browser automatically on first pageload

can also be changed by logging in

api.customUrl.description: Can set this up in config to connect with different api

api.timeoutAt.description: If the api doesn't response, this will be set to last date. If the api responds, this will be reset
